# SynapseAI Project Rules

## Code Style
- Use TypeScript for all files
- Use functional components with hooks
- Prefer named exports
- Use shadcn/ui components from components/ui
- Use TailwindCSS for styling
- Follow Next.js App Router conventions

## File Structure
- `/app` - Next.js pages (App Router)
- `/components` - React components
- `/lib` - Utilities, types, API functions
- `/store` - Zustand stores
- `/public` - Static assets

## Important Notes
- All API calls are mocked in lib/api.ts
- Replace mock functions with real API calls when backend is ready
- Logo should be placed in /public/logo.png
- Theme is managed via Zustand store and localStorage
